Subject: Leaving UCS



Dear friends and colleagues,



I will be leaving UCS at the end of May after completing several projects. =
I am looking forward to new challenges and opportunities with renewed energ=
y and commitment.



I intend to continue advocating for sustainable agriculture based on agroec=
ology, food sovereignty, and public crop improvement that broadly benefit s=
ociety. I also intend to continue analyzing the interface between science a=
nd society, including public policy and agricultural technologies such as g=
enetic engineering. I will be considering different possible venues for thi=
s work.



I want to take this opportunity to thank you for your important work and su=
ccessful collaborations over the years. I will never take for granted all t=
hat you do for food justice and sustainability.



I can be reached until the end of May at my USC phone and e-mail address. A=
fterwards, please stay in touch. I can be reached by email:Dgurian.sherman@=
gmail.com<mailto:Dgurian.sherman@gmail.com>, or on my cell phone: 240-676-4=
285.



